OL,10,Fprogramme is broadcast from Alexandra
OL,11,FPalace due to a power cut, which
OL,12,Fdisrupted the official launch (of the
OL,13,Fprogramme and channel) from TV Centre.
OL,14,
OL,15,FRichard Baker, from Alexandra Palace,
OL,16,Flinked together programmes for BBC One.
OL,17,
